The paper deals with computational complexity of queries based on frequent sets, which is a common problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the Maximum Entropy estimate, which is a popular technique in machine learning and statistics, falling under the category of learning (cs.LG). The problem of checking consistency is a fundamental problem in computer science and falls under the category of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS). Finally, the paper discusses the NP-completeness of the problem, which is a common topic in computational complexity theory (cs.CC).
